public class ElementInteractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.event.ComponentListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener

This class handles interaction of mouse and mouse motion with Element class and its components.
